The first was a car accident on New Year's Eve of 2002. He was the only one in the car when it crashed. Then he disappeared. It turned out a fan had him and it was like that movie "Misery". He was kept captive by fans, who wanted to keep him because he was famous. Now he was being held by aliens for the same reason.
Humanity needs Matt Damon. He is the only one who can save us from the evil's of the universe. Or at least that is what people think. The people call together a team to save Matt Damon. This team includes an Army General, two scientists, a psychic woman who can locate him by using time travel. The team is successful and they bring Matt Damon home.
